# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  World Cup 2026 Ticket Tracker — Environment Variables Template
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
#  1. Copy this file:   cp .env.example .env
#  2. Fill in your real values below
#  3. NEVER commit .env to git — add it to .gitignore
#
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


# ── SUPABASE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Find these in: Supabase Dashboard → Your Project → Settings → API

# Your project URL (looks like https://abcdefghijkl.supabase.co)
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co

# Anon/public key — safe to use for auth calls only
# Found under: Settings → API → Project API keys → anon public
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# Service role key — KEEP THIS SECRET, bypasses all Row Level Security
# Found under: Settings → API → Project API keys → service_role secret
# ⚠️  NEVER expose this in your frontend or commit it to git
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here


# ── RESEND (add when ready for email alerts) ──────────────────────────
# Sign up at https://resend.com — free tier: 3,000 emails/month
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_your-resend-api-key-here
# RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=alerts@yourdomain.com


# ── TICKET PLATFORM APIs (add when replacing the stub scraper) ────────
# StubHub Fan API — https://developer.stubhub.com
# STUBHUB_APP_TOKEN=your-stubhub-token-here

# SeatGeek Partner API — https://platform.seatgeek.com
# SEATGEEK_CLIENT_ID=your-seatgeek-client-id-here
# SEATGEEK_CLIENT_SECRET=your-seatgeek-client-secret-here

# Viagogo Affiliate API — https://developer.viagogo.net
# VIAGOGO_CLIENT_ID=your-viagogo-client-id-here
# VIAGOGO_CLIENT_SECRET=your-viagogo-client-secret-here
